metadata.name: Founder #1/16
metadata.description:
Square canvases drawn by generative code each time the page loads, which means that each piece can create an infinite amount of variations. GLFX have hierarchal and generational traits that can be referenced from and gamified, on-chain.

Celestials are the highest order in the class hierarchy, with Founders being the rarest, and include all the benefits of the lower classes plus more. More details on the official website and on Discord server.
